{"prompt": "Generate a website for a podcasting network. The website should be rustic and use red as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Redwood Podcasting Network</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --brand-color: #8B0000; /* Dark Red */\n            --secondary-color: #A0522D; /* Sienna */\n            --text-color: #F5DEB3; /* Wheat */\n            --background-color: #4E342E; /* Dark Brown */\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Georgia', serif;\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n\n        header {\n            background-color: var(--brand-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            padding: 2rem 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            border-bottom: 5px solid var(--secondary-color);\n        }\n\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 3rem;\n            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);\n        }\n\n        nav {\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 1rem;\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n        }\n\n        nav a {\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            text-decoration: none;\n            margin: 0 15px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            transition: color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        nav a:hover {\n            color: #FFFFFF;\n        }\n\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: 2rem auto;\n            padding: 20px;\n            background-color: rgba(78, 52, 46, 0.8); /* Slightly transparent dark brown */\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7);\n        }\n\n        h2 {\n            color: var(--brand-color);\n            text-align: center;\n            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;\n            text-shadow: 1px 1px 3px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);\n        }\n\n        .podcast-list {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));\n            gap: 20px;\n            margin-top: 20px;\n        }\n\n        .podcast-item {\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n            padding: 20px;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            border: 2px solid var(--secondary-color);\n            text-align: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        .podcast-item:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-5px);\n            box-shadow: 0 8px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7);\n        }\n\n        .podcast-item h3 {\n            margin-top: 0;\n            color: var(--brand-color);\n        }\n\n        .podcast-item p {\n            font-size: 0.9rem;\n        }\n\n        .podcast-item a {\n            display: inline-block;\n            margin-top: 15px;\n            padding: 10px 15px;\n            background-color: var(--brand-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            text-decoration: none;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        .podcast-item a:hover {\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n        }\n\n        footer {\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 2rem;\n            margin-top: 2rem;\n            background-color: var(--brand-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            border-top: 5px solid var(--secondary-color);\n        }\n\n        footer p {\n            margin: 0;\n        }\n\n        /* Simple animation for rusticity */\n        @keyframes flicker {\n            0%, 100% { opacity: 1; }\n            50% { opacity: 0.95; }\n        }\n\n        .podcast-item {\n            animation: flicker 4s infinite alternate ease-in-out;\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <header>\n        <h1>Redwood Podcasting Network</h1>\n    </header>\n\n    <nav>\n        <a href=\"#about\">About</a>\n        <a href=\"#podcasts\">Podcasts</a>\n        <a href=\"#contact\">Contact</a>\n    </nav>\n\n    <div class=\"container\" id=\"about\">\n        <h2>Welcome to Redwood</h2>\n        <p>Step into the warmth of the Redwood Podcasting Network. We bring you stories, insights, and conversations inspired by the timeless strength and natural beauty of the great outdoors. Our shows are crafted with care, much like a well-worn leather armchair by a crackling fire.</p>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"container\" id=\"podcasts\">\n        <h2>Our Latest Shows</h2>\n        <div class=\"podcast-list\">\n            <div class=\"podcast-item\">\n                <h3>Whispers of the Woods</h3>\n                <p>Explore the hidden histories and ecological wonders of our planet's ancient forests. From the giant sequoias to the temperate rainforests, journey with us through tales of survival, discovery, and the quiet power of nature.</p>\n                <a href=\"#\">Listen Now</a>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"podcast-item\">\n                <h3>Campfire Chronicles</h3>\n                <p>Gather 'round as we share personal stories, adventurous tales, and practical tips for embracing the wilderness. Each episode is like a night spent under the stars, filled with good company and captivating narratives.</p>\n                <a href=\"#\">Listen Now</a>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"podcast-item\">\n                <h3>The Woodworker's Bench</h3>\n                <p>Delve into the art and craft of woodworking. We celebrate the tradition, the innovation, and the satisfaction of working with natural materials to create something beautiful and lasting.</p>\n                <a href=\"#\">Listen Now</a>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"podcast-item\">\n                <h3>Trail Tales</h3>\n                <p>Embark on virtual expeditions with seasoned hikers, explorers, and nature enthusiasts. Discover breathtaking landscapes, challenging trails, and the profound connections forged in the wild.</p>\n                <a href=\"#\">Listen Now</a>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"container\" id=\"contact\">\n        <h2>Get In Touch</h2>\n        <p style=\"text-align: center;\">We'd love to hear from you! Whether you have a show idea, a question, or just want to share your thoughts, reach out to us through the following channels:</p>\n        <p style=\"text-align: center;\">Email: <a href=\"mailto:info@redwoodpodcasts.com\" style=\"color: var(--text-color); text-decoration: underline;\">info@redwoodpodcasts.com</a></p>\n        <p style=\"text-align: center;\">Follow us on <a href=\"#\" style=\"color: var(--text-color); text-decoration: underline;\">Social Media</a></p>\n    </div>\n\n    <footer>\n        <p>&copy; 2023 Redwood Podcasting Network. All rights reserved.</p>\n    </footer>\n\n</body>\n</html>\n"}